          <span class="font-bold">Successful approach:</span> Plan for 4-8 hours (simple site) or
          12-20 hours (complex site). AI generates draft (30 minutes). Customize content (2-4 hours).
          Adjust design (1-3 hours). Testing, revisions (1-3 hours). Realistic timeline = completion.
