          inquiries. Rewrote with specifics: "15 years experience, helped 127 clients, $2.3M
          revenue generated." Month 1 after rewrite: 89 visitors, 12 inquiries. Generic = invisible.
          Specific = converts.
        </p>
        <p class="font-bold text-orange-700">
          AI generates template. You make it real. Specificity sells.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-orange-50 p-8 border-[3px] mae-border">
